These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, cat, hamster, fish, rabbit, ferret
The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, dancer, entrepreneur, social-worker, lawyer, coach, paramedic
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the ferret##2
 2. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 3. the lawyer is on the right of the paramedic##1
 4. the owner of the fish is between the entrepreneur and the lawyer##2
 5. the dancer is on the right of the coach##1
 6. the dancer is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the manager is between the social-worker and the entrepreneur##2
 8. the dancer is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Pet   | hamster | guinea-pig | ferret | bird    | cat | fish   | rabbit    |
| Job         | coach  | dancer   | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur   | paramedic | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, librarian, software-developer, photographer, social-worker, dressmaker, nurse
House: ranch-style, palace, craftsman, gothic-revival, cottage, cape-cod, art-deco
1. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
2. the software-developer is between the dressmaker and the cape-cod house##2
3. the palace house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the nurse is on the right of the craftsman house##1
5. the librarian is in the middle##1
6. the cottage house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
7. the art-deco house is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the social-worker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
9. the photographer is on the right of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Job          | social-worker | software-developer | dressmaker | librarian | nurse | analyst      | photographer  |
| House   | cape-cod | gothic-revival  | art-deco     | craftsman     | cottage  | ranch-style | palace |

