.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, woodworking, gardening, dancing, filmmaking, rock-climbing, reading
House: art-deco, farmhouse, wooden, modern, craftsman, cottage, colonial
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the wooden house is on the left of the modern house##1
 3. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is the modern house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the art-deco house is between the colonial house and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the cottage house##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Hobby   | reading | filmmaking | puzzles | woodworking   | dancing | gardening | rock-climbing |
| House           | craftsman | cottage     | farmhouse     | wooden | modern   | art-deco   | colonial    |

