 3. the modern house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the cottage house is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is between the person who likes ebony and the modern house##2
 7. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person who likes yellow is the ranch-style house##1
10. the cottage house is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Color      | ebony    | apricot  | lavender  | white  | red      | black       | yellow |
| House   | cape-cod | gothic-revival | modern | tower | cottage | craftsman | ranch-style  |

