4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the cottage house is in the middle##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the colonial house is on the left of the modern house##1
8. the craftsman house is the person who's sport is tennis##1
9. the person who's sport is swimming is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | tennis      | swimming | snowboarding | weightlifting | parkour      | rowing      | sailing |
| House     | craftsman | futuristic | palace       | cottage | colonial | modern | victorian |

