3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing domino is between the person playing chess and the person who growsbellflower##2
7. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Flower     | dahlia | bellflower | sunflower | azalea | lily | daisy     | balloon-flower |
