 6. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the rabbit##2
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the turtle##2
