The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, november, august, june, april, september, december
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
7. the game-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the siglo-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person who's birthday is in september##2
9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | oliveros       | game         | bluemaster         | siglo   | montecristo        | havana |
| Birthday      | december | august | january | april | november | september | june  |

