.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-13::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, boat, bike, subway, van, tram
7 different games are played: bridge, billiard, mah-jongg, canasta, snooker, chess, go
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person driving the van is between the person playing bridge and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the subway##2
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person playing go is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Transport      | airplane   | boat | helicopter | van | subway | tram   | bike |
| Game   | canasta | mah-jongg | bridge     | snooker | go  | billiard | chess     |

