 7. the person watching family moviessy is the owner of the fish##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the turtle##2
10. the person watching family moviessy is in the middle##1

